{"tid":549400,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人打拍子發電有冇得諗?","createTime":"2018-02-03T14:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T18:28:27.000Z","uid":78141,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03787b2a2482dd74a23150be5fe968a9c9648500","tid":549400,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"睇演唱會時歌手想靜靜地唱首歌<br />\n<br />\n即使冇做手勢叫人打拍子<br />\n<br />\n點都會有班撚樣開始打拍子<br />\n<br />\n跟住又會有一班柒頭跟住黎拍手<br />\n<br />\n拍子唔準又破壞哂氣氛<br />\n<br />\n學校sing con又係咁<br />\n<br />\n即使唔係唱歌，跳舞有背景音樂都會打拍子<br />\n<br />\n不如發明舊嘢拍手發電<br />\n<br />\n開始前擺喺個位到<br />\n<br />\n電費減免在望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25c54b6a4e69a1b43cfd153ee11737b58ca792e","tid":549400,"uid":13421,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主，夠鐘訓喇"},{"pid":"5fb5160a7103ec048cfe0d3364962625c299849f","tid":549400,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"👏"},{"pid":"832256c124514d2358799801e10ce463558f4af3","tid":549400,"uid":76488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bc8c96e278517abbf9022614dc219750c0117a2","tid":549400,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:28:27.000Z","msg":"應該好似日本啲表演咁打call"}]}